import React from "react"; import '../assets/CSS/proejects.css' import {useGlobalState,setGlobalState} from '../components/componet.js' import graphml from '../assets/images/ML.png' import gif from '../assets/images/ezgif.com-crop.gif' import mariogif from '../assets/images/mario.gif' import Iphone from "../components/iphone"; import react from "../assets/images/react_1183672.png" import carving from '../assets/images/carving.gif' import seam from '../assets/images/seam.png' import back from '../assets/images/Background-Checks1.gif' import Computer from "../components/computer"; import web from '../assets/images/scrap.png' import Carousel from "../components/car"; function PProject(){ const[set] = useGlobalState('work'); const Tch = () =>{ setGlobalState('work',!set) } return(

Personal Projects

Here you see my personal projects

Perfect Snake

-Machine Learning

This Project was my primary intro into real machine learning and properly learning how to manage DNQ agents, multiple randomly generated actions as well as a reward system.

Worked with the pytorch library in order to create my own agent class set to play the game as well as used q-learning to train behavior over each game.

Worked with the pytorch library Q-Trainer in order to store and hold previous data to commit to long and short term memory as well as present realtime analysis with matplotlib.

Seam Carving

- Software-Engineering

Created a command line seam carver which takes in designed width and height in order to return a carved image within that given frame.

Analyzed the pixel variance between the layers of pixels from the given photo and the a calculated energy function to return given energy values of each pixel row.

The followed the path of least energy value to remove the pixels and condense the image to the desired size

Web Scrapping

-Data Science/ Software-Engineering

Worked on a real world applicable data sample in order to analysis margins of profitability for chocolate production

Created a Python web scrapping software to read a nested HTML and distribute into Pandas dictionaries.

Then identified quality related material to comparatively choose the best location and price, then through Matplotlib demonstrated correlation between rating and location as well as coco percentage.
